Other file types supported in <github organization>/.github

- FUNDING.yml: (sponsor buttons) does not seem relevant
- SUPPORT.md: Should we add a default one that links to
  theupdateframework/community/SUPPORT.md akin to CONTRIBUTING.m?
- ISSUE template(s):
  - Short preamble about organization structure and governance:
  - First read,
    - theupdateframework/.github/SECURITY.md, if you report a security issue
    - theupdateframework/.github/SUPPORT.md, if you have a question
  - Make sure you follow theupdateframework/.github/CODE_OF_CONDUCT.md

- PR template(s):
  - Short preamble about organization structure and governance:
  - First read,
    - theupdateframework/.github/SECURITY.md, if you want to fix an unreported security issue
    - theupdateframework/.github/CONTRIBUTING.md
  - Make sure you follow theupdateframework/.github/CODE_OF_CONDUCT.md
